{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"siteUrl":"http://ghost.local:8000","title":"InspireUI Document","description":"InspireUI document"}},"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Getting Started","date":null,"date_pretty":null,"path":null,"meta_title":"CeStore Web -Ecommerce Progressive Web Apps Template by ReactJS & MongoDB","meta_description":"React Native currently creates vibrant wave in mobile application development. “Write once, Run anywhere”, then you can effectively produce mobile app across all platforms including iOS & Android by one language with “Native effect”.","image":null,"next":null,"sidebar":"cestore-web","toc":null,"keywords":["cestore","cestore template","react-native","react-native app"]},"html":"<p>First please refer to this quick installing video guide: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HF1aQzVHEPQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HF1aQzVHEPQ</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"1-requirements\"><a href=\"#1-requirements\" aria-label=\"1 requirements permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Requirements</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Node.js >= 8</li>\n<li>MongoDB >= 3.2</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"2-run-application\"><a href=\"#2-run-application\" aria-label=\"2 run application permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. Run Application</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm start</code></pre></div>\n<p>Also, you can run application with PM2 and watch for modifications.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Install PM2 globally</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install pm2 -g</code></pre></div>\n<ol>\n<li>Run application</li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">pm2 start process.json</code></pre></div>\n<p>Open <a href=\"http://localhost:3000/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost:3000</a> to see your store.\nDashboard - <a href=\"http://localhost:3000/admin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost:3000/admin</a>\nAPI - <a href=\"http://localhost:3001/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">http://localhost:3001</a></p>\n<p>You can use following script for set up the product, the common use is <strong>yarn start</strong> and <strong>yarn build</strong></p>\n<table>\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th><code class=\"language-text\">npm run &lt;script&gt;</code></th>\n<th>Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">clean:admin</code></td>\n<td>Delete admin asset bundles.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">clean:store</code></td>\n<td>Delete store asset bundles.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">compile:dev</code></td>\n<td>Compiles the application to disk <strong>and watch</strong> (<code class=\"language-text\">~/dist</code> by default).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">compile</code></td>\n<td>Compiles the application to disk (<code class=\"language-text\">~/dist</code> by default).</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">webpack:admin:dev</code></td>\n<td>Assemble admin bundles <strong>and watch</strong>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">webpack:store:dev</code></td>\n<td>Assemble store bundles <strong>and watch</strong>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">webpack:admin:prod</code></td>\n<td>Assemble admin bundles.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">webpack:store:prod</code></td>\n<td>Assemble store bundles.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">theme:install</code></td>\n<td>Install theme from /public/.zip</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">theme:export</code></td>\n<td>Zip current theme to /public/.zip</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">theme:copy</code></td>\n<td>Compile theme and copy assets to /public/</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">theme:build:dev</code></td>\n<td>Refresh theme after modification <strong>and watch</strong>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">theme:build:prod</code></td>\n<td>Refresh theme after modification.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">build:dev</code></td>\n<td>Compile and assemble bundles <strong>and watch</strong>.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">build</code></td>\n<td>Compile and assemble bundles.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><code class=\"language-text\">start</code></td>\n<td>Start node server.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 id=\"3-configuration\"><a href=\"#3-configuration\" aria-label=\"3 configuration permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3. Configuration</h2>\n<p>By default MongoDB connection string is <code class=\"language-text\">mongodb://127.0.0.1:27017/shop</code></p>\n<p>Change it with environment variables</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">DB_HOST=255.255.255.255 \\\nDB_PORT=27017 \\\nDB_NAME=shop \\\nDB_USER=user \\\nDB_PASS=password \\\n# or SET a DB_URL with mongodb connection string(https://docs.mongodb.com/manual/reference/connection-string/)\nDB_URL=mongodb://db1.example.net:27017,db2.example.net:2500/?replicaSet=test\nnpm start</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"4-preparing-database\"><a href=\"#4-preparing-database\" aria-label=\"4 preparing database permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>4. Preparing Database</h2>\n<p>This script will:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>test MongoDB connection</li>\n<li>add default data from /mongodb_bk folder</li>\n<li>create basic indexes</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm run setup</code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"5-manage-the-product\"><a href=\"#5-manage-the-product\" aria-label=\"5 manage the product permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5. Manage the Product</h2>\n<p>After successful setup on step 1 then you can able to login to the admin dashboard to manage the products, select <strong>Product</strong> menu form the right side bar</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/195ef/admin2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 81.78070898598516%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"admin2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/efcfb/admin2.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/11053/admin2.png 200w,\n/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/1b42c/admin2.png 400w,\n/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/efcfb/admin2.png 800w,\n/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/d25cb/admin2.png 1200w,\n/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/22e61/admin2.png 1600w,\n/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/4b363/admin2.png 2400w,\n/static/68ea9e81787586f6b238d29c0885a333/195ef/admin2.png 2426w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<p>The Click the + button on correct top-right to create new product</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/f56a0/admin1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 82.8125%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"admin1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/efcfb/admin1.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/11053/admin1.png 200w,\n/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/1b42c/admin1.png 400w,\n/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/efcfb/admin1.png 800w,\n/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/d25cb/admin1.png 1200w,\n/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/22e61/admin1.png 1600w,\n/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/4b363/admin1.png 2400w,\n/static/1fb0ac8cf5c40775eff23c4888af1d44/f56a0/admin1.png 2432w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>\n<h2 id=\"6-general-settings\"><a href=\"#6-general-settings\" aria-label=\"6 general settings permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>6. General Settings</h2>\n<p>Go to Left menu side, select Setting and update the detail config from the side menu, example change teh default Currency from the General setting:</p>\n<p><a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/39132/admin3.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 800px;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 61.84100418410041%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    ></span>\n    <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"admin3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/efcfb/admin3.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/11053/admin3.png 200w,\n/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/1b42c/admin3.png 400w,\n/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/efcfb/admin3.png 800w,\n/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/d25cb/admin3.png 1200w,\n/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/22e61/admin3.png 1600w,\n/static/5cc93a57bde96fa3ba307cdf52900c3a/39132/admin3.png 2390w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n      />\n  </span>\n  </a></p>","fields":{"slug":"/cestore-web/getting-started/"},"timeToRead":3,"excerpt":"First please refer to this quick installing video guide:  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HF1aQzVHEPQ 1. Requirements Node.js >= 8 MongoDB…","fileAbsolutePath":"/Users/tony/Beo/inspireui-documents/docs/content/cestore-web/getting-started.md"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/cestore-web/getting-started/"}}